Somebody gets it.

00:45:21.070 --> 00:45:23.050
Requires zero accounting,
right?

00:45:23.050 --> 00:45:26.550
A ROSCA requires zero
accounting.

00:45:26.550 --> 00:45:28.910
Self-help group requires some
